  QL_FironeMini_HorseEnemy_Desc:
    contents:
      - text: "費羅尼草原是有名的馬匹產地。\n\n但是最近這裡被騎馬的"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 魯莽者們
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "佔據了，\n索艾很難過。\n\n如果能擊退"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 魯莽者們
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "，\n或許索艾就能重拾笑容。"
  QL_FironeMini_HorseEnemy_Exterminate:
    contents:
      - text: "你擊退了\n占據草原的"
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: red
      - text: 魯莽者們
      - control:
          kind: reset_colour
      - text: "！\n\n相信索艾知道這件事情以後，\n也能重拾笑容吧。"
  QL_FironeMini_HorseEnemy_Finish:
    contents:
      - text: "你擊退了\n占據草原的魯莽者們！\n\n告訴索艾這件事情以後，她非常開心。\n送給你毅力胡蘿蔔當作謝禮。\n\n這好像是馬最喜歡的食物。"
  QL_FironeMini_HorseEnemy_Name:
    contents:
      - text: 騎馬的魯莽者
